Today, we are celebrating women at Djerba Slush'D!

At Djerba Slush'D, the presence and contributions of extraordinary women were at the heart of our success. Their diverse expertise and leadership transformed our event into a melting pot of innovation and inspiration, highlighting the true potential of women in the ecosystem.

Salma Baghdadi, ignited the stage with her deep insights into Blue Tech. Her vision for sustainable solutions pushed us to think beyond the conventional.

The House of Ichigo women tribe: Louisa Zanoun & Alessia Balducci brought a wealth of knowledge from various fields – a testament to the power of diverse perspectives.

Our esteemed partners, M. Nejia Gharbi, @zeineb.chabchoub, @kimboubi, and Ghalia Bouarada showcased their dedication to fostering growth and collaboration. Their support and participation were crucial for the success of the event.

Elina Laurila and Stella Korpikuusi from the Slush HQ team brought their global expertise and vision, bridging international connections and opportunities.

The women of Djerba, with their vibrant energy and enthusiasm, were a constant reminder of the incredible potential that lies within our local, talented community. Khaoula Aroua, Ines Nafti, Thouraya Aroua, Siwar Maatoug.

Khouloud Torkhani, our Community & Marketing Manager, led the charge with exceptional grace and dedication. Alongside her were the remarkable women organizers—Judith Li-Kaiser, @idahuiskonen, @chaimaamraoui, and @trabelsi_maha17—whose hard work and commitment were instrumental in making Djerba Slush'D come to life.

We extend our heartfelt gratitude to these inspiring women for their invaluable contributions and leadership. Their knowledge, presence, and relentless efforts were the pillars of our event.

Thank you to each and every one of you for making Djerba Slush'D an unforgettable celebration of innovation and entrepreneurship!

Thank you to our partners for enabling this event!
